2015-03-17  MDW  Gemini Observatory

This module provides EPICS device driver and record support
for the Xycom XY240 and XY566 VME boards.

The original source code was obtained from --
XY240: http://www.aps.anl.gov/epics/download/modules/xycomDigital1-5.tar.gz
XY566: http://www.aps.anl.gov/epics/download/modules/xycomAnalog1-4.tar.gz

The code for each was modified to be EPICS OSI compliant.


The following note on XY566 issues is still relevant:
	XY566 Device & Driver Support
	=============================
There are a few compiler warnings when building this code.  These are
associated with some hairy callback scheme as far as I can see.  They
need to be looked at and proper function pointers declared and passed
around instead.  I don't have time (or the inclination) to do so just
now.

